{"tid":2315377,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許智峯流亡︱戶口凍結機制惹疑惑 銀行反洗錢部：受制於警方","createTime":"2020-12-07T06:56:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T06:56:55.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b36f76b9338f9f3b9da438f32184bd9c355ce284","tid":2315377,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:56:55.000Z","msg":"有不願具名的銀行反洗錢部門高層指出，銀行凍結賬戶或有兩種可能性，一是警方已有法庭頒發的限制令或已羅列涉及罪行，二是銀行考慮到信譽風險，審慎起見預先凍結賬戶，「通常是已從警方方面得知涉及犯罪行為，而警方正同步向法庭申請限制令」。他又指出，原則上受影響客戶可要求銀行安排直接與相關警員聯絡了解事情。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201207/BI7UV7BDNVCKZOLWAEHDI7BFBE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201207%2FBI7UV7BDNVCKZOLWAEHDI7BFBE%2F&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTmztmS%2FM%2FHF6fRawSWcCn68%3D&h=7022f60f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201207%2FBI7UV7BDNVCKZOLWAEHDI7BFBE%2F&h=9d55f631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201207/BI7UV7BDNVCKZOLWAEHDI7BFBE/</a>"}]}